----------------------------- KEYBOARD CONTROLS ----------------------------

[F9]         - order screen
[ESC]        - exit

[SPACE BAR]  - fire weapon
[UPARROW]    - move forward     [CTRL] [UPARROW]    - move forward fast
[DOWNARROW]  - move backward    [CTRL] [DOWNARROW]  - move backward fast
[LEFTARROW]  - turn left        [CTRL] [LEFTARROW]  - strafe left
[RIGHTARROW] - turn right       [CTRL] [RIGHTARROW] - strafe right

[D] - duck
[F] - jump
[T] - transport slave to safty (must be near slave)

[CTRL] [ALT] [I] - God mode toggle

[M]     - toggle music on/off
[+]/[-] - enlarge/shrink view window
[1]/[2] - increase/decrease turning sensitivity
[3]/[4] - increase/decrease movement sensitivity
[P]     - display posistion
[Pause] - pause/resume game play

[F1] - save game to slot 1      [ALT] [F1] - restore game from slot 1
[F2] - save game to slot 2      [ALT] [F2] - restore game from slot 2
[F3] - save game to slot 3      [ALT] [F3] - restore game from slot 3
[f4] - save game to slot 4      [ALT] [F4] - restore game from slot 4

[F5] - select weapon
[F6] - toggle low/high resolution
[F7] - toggle stereographic mode on/off (only in registered version)


------------------------------ MOUSE CONTROLS ------------------------------

[LEFT BUTTON]   - fire
[RIGHT BUTTON]  - move forward / open doors
slide forward   - move forward
slide back      - move backward
slide left      - turn left
slide right     - turn right

NOTE: If you experience difficulty playing the game with a mouse, make sure 
your mouse is configured to run in non-accelerated mode.  To change your
mouse configuration refer to the documentation that came with your 
computer/mouse.


----------------------------- JOYSTICK CONTROLS ----------------------------

push forward    - move forward
pull back       - move backward
push left       - turn left
push right      - turn right


-------------------------- GRAVIS GAME-PAD CONTROLS ------------------------

[RED BUTTON]    - strafe left
[GREEN BUTTON]  - strafe right
[BLUE BUTTON]   - fire
[YELLOW BUTTON] - duck

